{
  "stem": "11723.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I turned literally green.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was so afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't stay in one place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was shaking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my sister, however, she was two years old, and she just learn to speak.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she had a bunting bag, and every time there was an air raid, she had to be in the bunting bag, and then she was safe.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So she was yelling, quick, quick!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Get me the bag, the bag, the bag!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And once they put her in the bag, my mother zipped her up, she says to me, don't worry, Agica, nothing is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The plane won't thrown bomb.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The plane won't throw bomb.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "No bomb from plane.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she was happy as a clam sitting in her bunting bag.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I was deathly pale, and my father decided that he wasn't going to take me down to the basement of the apartment building to the shelter, but he would take me across the street.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And across the street was a school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the principal of the school was a big Nazi, Hungarian Nazi, and we went in there and the principal was making all sorts of speeches.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I'm sure that my father was thinking, oh my God, if anybody recognizes us or somebody comes in and asks for papers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "All they have to do is ask him to drop his pants.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Nobody was circumcised unless they were Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But fortunately my great fortune was that I did not look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Nobody thought I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And somehow we got away with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The air raid ended, my father took me back upstairs, and he went home to his place-- home, whenever he was hiding.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then every day my mother and Uncle Rega took us to different places trying to place us.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
